				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Teaching the Sochi Olympics | Science, Health and Math</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Jennifer Cutraro and Patrick Honner			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-02-12T19:08:52+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">February 12, 2014 2:08 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">February 12, 2014 2:08 pm</span>		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><a href="//www.nytimes.com/newsgraphics/2014/sochi-olympics/ski-jumping.html"><div class="w592"><figure class="media photo promo" itemprop="associatedMedia" itemscope="" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/02/08/multimedia/oly-preview-skijump-LN/oly-preview-skijump-tmagArticle.jpg" itemtype="//schema.org/ImageObject" role="group"><span class="visually-hidden">Photo</span><div class="image"><img itemprop="url" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/02/08/multimedia/oly-preview-skijump-LN/oly-preview-skijump-tmagArticle.jpg" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/02/08/multimedia/oly-preview-skijump-LN/oly-preview-skijump-tmagArticle.jpg" id="100000002706474" width="592" height="376" alt="&lt;a href=&quot;//www.nytimes.com/newsgraphics/2014/sochi-olympics/ski-jumping.html&quot;&gt;Related Interactive Graphic&lt;/a&gt;"   /><meta itemprop="height" content="376"><meta itemprop="width" content="592"></div><figcaption class="caption" itemprop="description"><span class="caption-text"><a href="//www.nytimes.com/newsgraphics/2014/sochi-olympics/ski-jumping.html">Related Interactive Graphic</a></span><span class="credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder"><span class="visually-hidden">Credit</span> Mike Hewitt/Getty Images</span></figcaption></figure></div></a></p>
<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//learning.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/02/12/teaching-the-sochi-olympics-science-health-and-math/" data-title="Teaching the Sochi Olympics | Science, Health and Math" data-description="The 2014 Winter Olympics offer a chance for students to dig into some of the more technical subjects. ">
